Short: BOOPSI gadget class implementation

Implementation of the Virtual Coordinate Box (VCB) BOOPSI class

VERSION
	1.0 beta

DISTRIBUTION
	This distribution includes the following files
		README				this file
		README.lib			some comments on the scanned library
		callhook.c			support (probably not needed by others than Aztec)
		domethod.c			support (probably not needed by others than Aztec)
		hookentry.asm		support (probably not needed by others than Aztec)
		makefile			makefile to create the scanned library
		setuphook.c			support (probably not needed by others than Aztec)
		tags				vi tags
		test				test example
		test.c				source of test example
		vcb.doc				the main documentation
		vcb.h				the public header file (needed by client programs)
		vcb.lib				the scanned library for Manx/Aztec Linker
		vcb.n				nro source of documentation
		vcb_private.h		private header file
		vcbclass.c			the VCB class module
		vcx.h				public header file of VCX class (undocumented)
		vcx_private.h		private header file
		vcxclass.c			the VCX class module (undocumented)
		vcxtest				test example for VCX class
		vcxtest.c			source of test example for VCX class

